snippet.title: Wunderling DX - Official Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
Wunderling DX is a non-stop puzzle platformer and the world's first "goomba simulator"! Race against the clock, beat tricky puzzles, collect shiny items, and please your evil overlord!

Buy Wunderling DX on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/Wunderling-1731548.html
